# Maintain your connection

Now that you are running GOV.UK Verify as part of your live service, you must ensure that you:

* [rotate your encription and signing keys](LINK)
* keep your [Verify Service Provider](https://github.com/alphagov/verify-service-provider/releases) up to date

You can also keep up to date with the [status of GOV.UK Verify][status] by subscribing to updates.

